====Examples====

Begin transaction to specified address

'''NEO:AeNkbJdiMx49kBStQdDih7BzfDwyTNVRfb'''


Begin transaction of unspecified amount of NEO

'''NEO:AeNkbJdiMx49kBStQdDih7BzfDwyTNVRfb?assetID=c56f33fc6ecfcd0c225c4ab356fee59390af8560be0e930faebe74a6daff7c9b'''

Begin transaction to specified address of 1 NEO

'''NEO:AeNkbJdiMx49kBStQdDih7BzfDwyTNVRfb?assetID=c56f33fc6ecfcd0c225c4ab356fee59390af8560be0e930faebe74a6daff7c9b&amount=1.0'''

Begin transaction to specified address of 1 NEO with transaction attribute Remark = "Hello"

'''NEO:AeNkbJdiMx49kBStQdDih7BzfDwyTNVRfb?assetID= c56f33fc6ecfcd0c225c4ab356fee59390af8560be0e930faebe74a6daff7c9b&amount=1.0&attributes=0xf0=9048656c6c6f'''

This should be sufficient to facilitate transfer of native NEO assets safely.

